{"tid":921183,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Twins化身光之美少女 以7位數字任香港區代言人(圖)","createTime":"2018-11-29T10:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T21:15:38.000Z","uid":89627,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7cfae17e547465c7d7f47cb850449d7dd5578a","tid":921183,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"日本某著名動畫製作公司製作的超人氣動畫《光之美少女》(Pretty Cure)，將於7月16日(星期日)在翡翠台隆重播映。為隆重其事，該公司及日本著名玩具商特別邀請偶像組合Twins主唱主題曲《光之美少女跳躍登場》並成為其代言人。阿Sa代表美墨莎莎--黑天使十四歲的初中生，性格開朗、剛強、極富正義感。阿嬌則代表雪城乃香--雪天使同是十四歲的初中生，乃香的性格卻是截然不同。表面性格穩重，成績相當優秀，相當博學，被稱為學識女王並常埋首在各種實驗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">此次Twins以7位數字任香港區代言人，酬勞當然相當滿意</span></strong>，此外拍攝全新MV也花費不少，動用了六位數字製作佈景外，還需要製作大量後期電腦特技效果，可以說是不惜功本。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqylss/2006-06/23/xin_240603231123690890334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fhqylss%2F2006-06%2F23%2Fxin_240603231123690890334.jpg&h=15b3d765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqylss/2006-06/23/xin_2406032311234712412533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fhqylss%2F2006-06%2F23%2Fxin_2406032311234712412533.jpg&h=ee56cf67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發覺想當年twins真係好吸金, <br />\n如果無黑鮑事件的話, 而家嘅twins可以走到去幾遠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39962bba988b7c816ad2fa0c8dd9a15fb29a93e8","tid":921183,"uid":117286,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"第一輯Pretty cure 真係無敵，仲要搵埋Twins 係絕配"},{"pid":"5d5ee5d9a316e0eb6eeb4ad10eda18a9e49ec4cd","tid":921183,"uid":92230,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"顏色好似調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452c9129f399cb120e3c6f0767b80a4d9d4b8b05","tid":921183,"uid":215111,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d5ee5d9a316e0eb6eeb4ad10eda18